{% extends '../base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About LokiPass{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 min-h-screen">
        <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-12">
            <article>
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold dark:text-white mb-4">About LokiPass</h1>
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <p class="text-lg mb-3 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Welcome to LokiPass, your reliable tool for generating secure passwords! We understand the
                        importance of safeguarding your online accounts and protecting your sensitive information from unauthorized
                        access. With LokiPass, you can effortlessly create strong, unique passwords that meet the highest security
                        standards.</p>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold dark:text-white mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <p class="text-lg mb-3 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">At LokiPass, our mission is to empower individuals and businesses to enhance their online
                        security through robust password generation. We believe that a strong password is the first line of defense
                        against cyber threats, and we are committed to providing a simple and reliable solution for creating passwords
                        that are virtually unbreakable.</p>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold dark:text-white mb-4">How LokiPass Works</h2>
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <p class="text-lg mb-3 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">LokiPass utilizes advanced algorithms to generate complex passwords that are both secure and
                        memorable. Our algorithm takes into account various factors such as password length, character types
                        (uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and special characters), and customizable options to suit your specific needs.
                        We ensure that every password generated by LokiPass is unique, ensuring maximum protection for your
                        accounts.</p>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold dark:text-white mb-4">Key Features</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-500 list-disc list-inside dark:text-gray-400 pl-6 mb-8">
                    <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold">Secure and Reliable:</span> Our password generator employs industry-standard encryption techniques to
                        ensure the highest level of security for your generated passwords.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold">Customizable Options:</span> You have full control over the complexity of your passwords. Choose from
                        various options such as length, character types, and the inclusion of special characters.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold">Memorable Passwords:</span> LokiPass generates passwords that are not only secure but also easier to
                        remember, making it convenient for you to access your accounts without compromising security.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold">Instant Generation:</span> With LokiPass, you can quickly generate passwords on the fly, eliminating
                        the hassle of coming up with strong passwords yourself.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold">No User Data Storage:</span> We prioritize your privacy. LokiPass does not store any of the passwords
                        generated, ensuring that your sensitive information remains confidential.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold dark:text-white mb-4">Get Started with LokiPass</h2>
                <ol class="space-y-1 text-gray-500 list-decimal list-inside dark:text-gray-400 pl-6 mb-8">
                    <li class="text-lg">Choose the desired password length.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg">Select the character types you want to include.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg">Customize any additional options according to your preference.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg">Click on the "Generate Password" button.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg">Voila! Your secure password will be displayed on the screen.</li>
                    <li class="text-lg">Copy and use the password to enhance the security of your online accounts.</li>
                </ol>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold dark:text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
                <p class="text-lg mb-8 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">We value your feedback and suggestions. If you have any questions, concerns, or ideas for
                    improving LokiPass, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. You can contact our team by sending an email to
                    <a href="mailto:support@lokipass.com" class="text-blue-500 font-bold">support@lokipass.com</a> or by using the contact form
                    on our website.</p>
                <p class="text-lg mb-3 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Thank you for choosing LokiPass to strengthen your online security. We're here to help you protect
                    what matters most!</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
